@node "QuickSetUp" "Quick Installation"
@next "Main"
@prev "Main"
 Quick Installation:
 ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

 1. Copy the MQwkID Directory to the DOORS: assignment.
 2. Make sure the BBS Location is configured in the MEBBSNet Network
    Definitions.
 3. Add the door to a menu as a MultiRunDoor.

   Example:

      Function D
         MultiRunDoor "DOORS:MQwkID/MQwkID"
      end

 4. Read the complete documention for information on customizing MQwkID.
@endnode

